{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_019pmvExVDNPUn4vokjvzc6G","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The T12 commit only updated `.ralph/` files. `NotificationToast.tsx` was NEVER committed. The agent wrote it to disk but didn't stage it, so when the worktree was merged, the file was lost (untracked files are not included in git commits unless staged).\n\nNow I understand the root cause: **the agent writes the file using the Write tool but doesn't run `git add` to stage it before the orchestrator commits.** The orchestrator only commits staged/tracked files that have changed, so the new untracked file gets lost.\n\nActually wait - let me look at this more carefully. The commit `acfdc80` shows only `.ralph/` files were in the \"T12 automated progress\" commit. And `1395f2b` is a merge of those two commits. \n\nSo the issue is clear: when the agent writes a new file in the worktree but fails to stage it with `git add`, the orchestrator's commit only captures already-tracked files and metadata changes, leaving the unstaged file behind to be discarded when the worktree is cleaned up.\n\nThe Ralph rules explicitly allow agents to stage files with `git add` for specific files they create, so I should add a new task that directly instructs the agent to both write the NotificationToast.tsx file and stage it immediately. I'll also reset the overall status back to IN_PROGRESS and update the progress log. Before doing that though, I want to pull the existing source files and do a thorough review of all the other acceptance criteria to make sure there aren't similar issues elsewhere.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1433,"cache_read_input_tokens":62219,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1433},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"bd7e2ef3-8758-4795-9502-9148468c5ae7","uuid":"d0e7eb45-c9d9-49b0-bb52-8530cd1d6cd3"}
